nodes.text: Making Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Unseen!

Making Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Unseen! is a series of six-page articles by J. W. Rinzler, which shows never-before-seen images of Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi from the Lucasfilm Archives, including behind-the-scenes photos and concept art. Some of these images were included in Rinzler's book, The Making of Return of the Jedi. The first article was published in Star Wars Insider 140.
